#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104owb1665702565740.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/owb1665702565740.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/owb1665702565740.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"owb1665702565740\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n       $equalStructRefs\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"owb1665702565740___equalstructrefs_262169\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Checks whether two variables of type struct reference the same physical Struct.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"owb1665702565740__topic_d82649e1_d82650e1_d82651e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"owb1665702565740__p_d82652e1_d82653e1_d82654e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$equalStructRefs</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct1</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct2</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"owb1665702565740__topic_d54547e1_d54548e1_d54549e1_d54550e1_d54551e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d323402e82\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"owb1665702565740__p_d82658e1_d82659e1_d82660e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct1</var> and <var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct2</var>—variables of type <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">struct</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"owb1665702565740__topic_d54552e1_d54553e1_d54554e1_d54555e1_d54556e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d323402e100\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"owb1665702565740__p_d82664e1_d82665e1_d82666e1\">Returns true if, and only if, <var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct1</var> and <var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct2</var> refer to the same Struct; in all other cases it returns False.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"owb1665702565740__topic_d54557e1_d54558e1_d54559e1_d54560e1_d54561e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d323402e115\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"owb1665702565740__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"owb1665702565740__topic_d54562e1_d54563e1_d54564e1_d54565e1_d54566e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d323402e125\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"owb1665702565740__p_d82676e1_d82677e1_d82678e1\">Use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$equalStructRefs</span> to compare Structs by reference. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jih1665702565816.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jih1665702565816.html\" title=\"You can compare struct variables with one another to check whether they have the same value, reference the same object, or have the same structure and annotations.\">Comparing Structs</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"owb1665702565740__section_mys_rjy_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d323402e147\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$equalStructRefs</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"owb1665702565740__pre_ds3_sjy_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">if ($equalStructRefs(vStructA, vStructB) != 1)\n &lt;do something&gt; \nendif</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jih1665702565816.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Comparing Structs</a><p>You can compare struct variables with one another to check whether they have the same value, reference the same object, or have the same structure and annotations.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530763\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530763\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$equalStructRefs Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $equalStructRefs Checks whether two variables of type struct reference the same physical Struct. $equalStructRefs ( Struct1 , Struct2 ) Parameters Struct1 and Struct2 —variables of type struct Return Values Returns true if, and only if, Struct1 and Struct2 refer to the same Struct; in all other cases it returns False. Use Allowed in all component types. Description Use $equalStructRefs to compare Structs by reference. For more information, see Comparing Structs . Example: Using $equalStructRefs if ($equalStructRefs(vStructA, vStructB) != 1) <do something> endif Copy Related Links Comparing Structs You can compare struct variables with one another to check whether they have the same value, reference the same object, or have the same structure and annotations. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}